WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
Conversation C

00:03.000 --> 00:06.000
Hello, is that Darming?

00:06.000 --> 00:09.000
Yes, High Lingling.

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
Hey, are you free tomorrow?

00:12.000 --> 00:16.000
Yes, I think so. What's happening?

00:16.000 --> 00:20.000
The Nature Club is going on a trip to the Forest Park.

00:20.000 --> 00:22.000
Would you like to come?

00:22.000 --> 00:24.000
Great, I'd love to.

00:24.000 --> 00:27.000
When and where are we going to meet?

00:27.000 --> 00:34.000
At the school gate at 7-10, then we'll go to the Forest Park by bus.

00:34.000 --> 00:37.000
The bus leaves at 7-30.

00:37.000 --> 00:40.000
It'll take us 40 minutes to get there.

00:40.000 --> 00:43.000
Do I need to bring anything?

00:43.000 --> 00:48.000
Oh yes. Everyone's going to bring their favourite food and drink.

00:48.000 --> 00:51.000
We're going to have a picnic in the forest.

00:51.000 --> 00:55.000
Great, I can't wait. I'm sure we'll have a good time.

00:55.000 --> 01:01.000
See you tomorrow. Remember, 10 past 7 in the morning.

01:01.000 --> 01:04.000
Don't worry, I won't be late.

